# Changelog

To install the unreleased tmuxp version, see {ref}`developmental-releases`.

[pip](https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/):

```console
$ pip install --user --upgrade --pre tmuxp
```

[uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/getting-started/features/#python-versions):

```console
$ uv add tmuxp --prerelease allow
```

[uvx](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/guides/tools/):

```console
$ uvx --from 'tmuxp' --prerelease allow tmuxp
```

[pipx](https://pypa.github.io/pipx/docs/):

```console
$ pipx install \
    --suffix=@next \
    --pip-args '\--pre' \
    --force \
    'tmuxp'
```

Run the developmental install with:

```console
$ tmuxp@next load yoursession
```

## tmuxp 1.70.0 (Yet to be released)

